These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bluemaster, swisher, dannemann
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, family, mystery
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, lacrosse, water-polo
House: cape-cod, victorian, futuristic, townhouse
 1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##8
 2. the cape-cod house is not to the left of the cape-cod house##8
 3. the townhouse house is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
 5. the cape-cod house is not to the right of the cape-cod house##8
 6. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the bluemaster-smoker is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5
 8. the person watching mystery movies is between the victorian house and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
 9. the townhouse house is the person watching family movies##1
10. the townhouse house is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
11. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the person watching animation movies##3
12. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere to the right of the bluemaster-smoker##5
13. the person watching family movies is not to the left of the townhouse house##8
14. the bluemaster-smoker is the futuristic house##1
15. the bluemaster-smoker is not the person who's sport is ice-hockey##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Cigar         | oliveros     | bluemaster   | dannemann | swisher |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery   | animation   | family  |
| Sport         | ice-hockey  | lacrosse  | water-polo  | cycling |
| House     | cape-cod    | futuristic | victorian     | townhouse    |

