.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, weightlifting, basketball, sailing
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, hiking, dancing, card-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, indie, salsa, trance
4 different pets are kept: dog, frog, goldfish, rabbit
 1. the fan of salsa is between the owner of the dog and the fan of indie##2
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
 3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
 4. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the fan of indie##8
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is not to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##8
 7. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the rabbit##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of house is the owner of the frog##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
11. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the fan of salsa##8
12. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
13. the fan of trance is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##5
14. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the fan of salsa##3
15. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left or far right##3
16. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
17. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
18. the person who's hobby is hiking is not to the right of the owner of the frog##8
19. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4   |
| Sport      | swimming | basketball | sailing  | weightlifting  |
| Hobby          | card-games     | hiking | fishing | dancing  |
| Music-Genre   | indie    | salsa  | trance | house |
