The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, rowing, tennis
 1. the person drinking milk is not the person driving the subway##6
 2. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
 3. the person eating plum is the person driving the airplane##1
 4. the person eating banana is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the bike##2
 5. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 6. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person eating banana##8
 7. the person drinking coffee is in an odd position##4
 8. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 9. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
10. the person driving the bike is the person who's sport is basketball##1
11. the person who's sport is golf is not to the right of the person eating apple##8
12. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
13. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
14. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
15. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |         2          |    3    |    4     |
