There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, nigerian, thai
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, reggae, dubstep, ambient
 1. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5
 2. the fan of punk is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in august##8
 3. the fan of punk is not to the left of the person drinking water##8
 4. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
 5. the fan of dubstep is the nigerian##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the dutch##8
 7. the person drinking sprite is not the thai##6
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the fan of dubstep and the person drinking sprite##7
 9. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
10. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
11. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
12. the person who's birthday is in september is not the argentine##6
13. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
14. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
15. the fan of punk is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage      | sprite    | water   | tea        | iced-tea  |
| Birthday           | august     | september | january | february  |
