The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, folk, reggae, soul
House: cape-cod, modern, futuristic, ranch-style
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, quad-bike, snowmobile
 1. the person eating radish is the ranch-style house##1
 2. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 3. the person eating carrot is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 4. the person eating onionmelon is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
 7. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
 8. the person driving the boat is not to the right of the modern house##8
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the futuristic house##1
10. the person eating carrot is not to the right of the fan of folk##8
11. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person eating onion##1
12. the person driving the snowmobile is in an odd position##4
13. the fan of reggae is somewhere to the left of the modern house##5

